</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200803/326a35ef94404e8da9a7e2eacd566b85.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200803/30bb16774725411b981c5ca3146dacab.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>第十七届大沥凤池铝门窗建筑装饰博览会一连四天，市场交投活跃，六大展区共计1600多个商铺和展位的参展商收获满满。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200803/6942c60bb7c740ecb3d2ca3c46b8b810.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
